import { Box , Typography  } from '@mui/system'
import React from 'react'

const City = () => {
  return (
    <Box pt={3} p={3}  mt={3}>
         <Typography variant='h5' component='div' fontWeight={600}>
        Trending Projects
         </Typography>
        <Typography variant='subtitle2' color='#747474'>
            Most sought-after projects in Thane
        </Typography>
        
    </Box>
  )
}

export default City
